{"tid":2478954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"智能叛變｜中國機械狗列隊動作一致短片上載Twitter 　引外國網民關注","createTime":"2021-04-07T12:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T19:49:02.000Z","uid":271829,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"a49fb328ae97b572455962234c004f53062f4485","tid":2478954,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/disclosetv/status/1378441122545078273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdisclosetv%2Fstatus%2F1378441122545078273&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=b2f2a127\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdisclosetv%2Fstatus%2F1378441122545078273&h=85e2b94c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/disclosetv/status/1378441122545078273</a><br />\n<br />\n中國的宇樹科技(Unitree Robotics)上載其研發的機械狗Aliengo一段短片到Twitter，引起外國網民關注。片中數十隻機械狗「列隊」排在一起，並同時做出一致動作，行動整齊如軍隊。有網友認為，「中國正試圖軍事化此技術，以入侵美國。」另有人擔心科幻電影裡的智能機械人叛變攻擊人類情節或真的會發生，「此短片令我想起《黑鏡》(英劇)其中一集。」他所指的應該是人類遭機械狗追殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1617709622_7o-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1617709622_7o-1280w.jpg&h=b248bfc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n短片中的機械狗動作一致。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1617709624_TL-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1617709624_TL-1280w.jpg&h=f73a7a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行動整齊如軍隊。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1617709620_mv-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1617709620_mv-1280w.jpg&h=47067509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民認為，中國正軍事化AI技術，以入侵美國。(互聯網)\\<br />\n<br />\n網民：中美AI技術距離僅12小時<br />\nAliengo可負荷11磅重物，適合用於工廠或其他體力勞動工作，對人類應不構成威脅。但有網友就關注，Aliengo顯示中國的人工智能(AI)技術已追貼美國，「在AI上，中國落後美國多少？約12小時」。美國國防部聯合人工智能中心主任、海軍陸戰隊中將Michael Groen上月曾稱，中國大力推行「中國製造2025」，目標是在2030年主宰AI領域，他認為美國國防部須做好準備，要快速和全面應對。"},{"pid":"6a7513cbe96fcafc4ae064d4a4e06344f663e5a4","tid":2478954,"uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"移動炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e765d241d0cf3259cd47944b01f7c501c0eeb091","tid":2478954,"uid":201604,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e402e8439441033b6dabac201c4c7142507f87b","tid":2478954,"uid":301820,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"德國智能工業不斷幫支那研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59d4fcb2051bc560dfe9b8d8abe94cd433eb818","tid":2478954,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:43:44.000Z","msg":"多謝弊燈"},{"pid":"34271720032f875d71edd565bbeb23106532bad2","tid":2478954,"uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"最失敗係個音樂 .. 點解唔配中式音樂呢"},{"pid":"092bb466f4a933ce3699f6c59f0441399c97d841","tid":2478954,"uid":10890,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"屌抄鳩Boston dynamics隻Spot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b35689475eda808ff0ba48e1b6206528a7c06d","tid":2478954,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e402e8439441033b6dabac201c4c7142507f87b","tid":2478954,"uid":301820,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"德國智能工業不斷幫支那研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" clas