叛變攻擊人類情節或真的會發生，「此短片令我想起《黑鏡》(英劇)其中一集。」他所指的應該是人類遭機械狗追殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1617709622_7o-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1617709622_7o-1280w.jpg&h=b248bfc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n短片中的機械狗動作一致。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1617709624_TL-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1617709624_TL-1280w.jpg&h=f73a7a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行動整齊如軍隊。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/4/1617709620_mv-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F4%2F1617709620_mv-1280w.jpg&h=47067509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民認為，中國正軍事化AI技術，以入侵美國。(互聯網)\\<br />\n<br />\n網民：中美AI技術距離僅12小時<br />\nAliengo可負荷11磅重物，適合用於工廠或其他體力勞動工作，對人類應不構成威脅。但有網友就關注，Aliengo顯示中國的人工智能(AI)技術已追貼美國，「在AI上，中國落後美國多少？約12小時」。美國國防部聯合人工智能中心主任、海軍陸戰隊中將Michael Groen上月曾稱，中國大力推行「中國製造2025」，目標是在2030年主宰AI領域，他認為美國國防部須做好準備，要快速和全面應對。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T19:22:38.000Z","msg":"唔怕<br />\n中國時差快12小時"},{"pid":"96dd61041ddcad89831cce7ae4473a935964f410","tid":2478954,"uid":302204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34df389711435cb54b3b878e48224fc72e0083f1","tid":2478954,"uid":184022,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"65628e741371acbcab1d539b807530b1e9c92bb8","tid":2478954,"uid":30104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85edf57c65e2f26beff1c3ffb8fb7b39237d0271","tid":2478954,"uid":184022,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:53:35.000Z","msg":"如果伊朗買咗，2，300隻，每隻揹10磅炸藥衝美軍基地，都有用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:47:43.000Z","msg":"你整架搖控車衝埋去已經得啦<br />\n行得快過隻狗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"隻狗就係可以全地型高速行走，跨過障礙物<img s